## Configuration

Set the following environment variables:

```bash
export OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
export PORT=8080
```

## Running

```bash
cargo run
```

## Docker

```bash
docker build -t ai-microservice .
docker run -p 8080:8080 ai-microservice
```
